==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: cart load
<hw>cart load</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>as
much as will fill or load a cart; the quantity that a cart holds. In
excavating and carting sand, gravel, earth, etc., one third of a cubic
yard of the material before it is loosened is estimated to be a cart
load.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cartman</ent>⟦br⟧
